{"tid":762942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民發現國旗倒掛半降　南通機場：風力作用，迅速調整","createTime":"2018-07-31T16:46:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T04:32:17.000Z","uid":38651,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cc5dbd4eadb8547903a6ef176996eff3ed7295fd","tid":762942,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T16:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/01/004605_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2F004605_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=684b9a09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒報道，有網民發現江蘇省南通興東機場倒掛國旗，且國旗未升到旗杆頂，猶如「下半旗」。目擊民眾質疑機場「有損南通形象」。<br />\n<br />\n機場其後在官方微博稱，根據監控錄像，工作人員今早7時20分將國旗「正常升至旗杆頂部」，但旗幟上部未完全扣緊，「在風力作用下造成意外」，職員發現後已迅速調整。機場指會汲取教訓，「舉一反三」，杜絕同類事件。<br />\n<br />\n（江海通報/南通機場官方微博）<br />\n<br />\n咩風力作用可以做到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb0bffc339e5e5f50381d9990c24cc2760c6722","tid":762942,"uid":176366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T18:08:56.000Z","msg":"今次仆街了"},{"pid":"333ce82c228c9a9f8565600c063129f1bcceb7af","tid":762942,"uid":41245,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T18:34:21.000Z","msg":"支那真係慣性講大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b14f97fc6a7b70e6ab2b328c534f48289620d9b","tid":762942,"uid":62011,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T18:36:17.000Z","msg":"咁係咪即係話連個天都反支那？"},{"pid":"4f75b6f1b6604a3d808d6c56c309a08b5b9c5544","tid":762942,"uid":44689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b14f97fc6a7b70e6ab2b328c534f48289620d9b","tid":762942,"uid":62011,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T18:36:17.000Z","msg":"咁係咪即係話連個天都反支那？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T18:38:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">天</span></span>